resources.title: Introduction to Programming
resources.description: Learn the fundamentals of programming and basic syntax.
resources.fullDescription: This comprehensive introduction covers programming basics, variables, data types, and control structures. Students will learn how to write simple programs and understand the logic behind programming concepts.

resources.title: Calculus Fundamentals
resources.description: Basic concepts of differential calculus and limits.
resources.fullDescription: Dive into the world of calculus with this detailed lesson on limits, derivatives, and their applications. Understand the fundamental theorem of calculus and practice with real-world problems.

resources.title: Data Structures and Algorithms
resources.description: Introduction to arrays, linked lists, and basic algorithms.
resources.fullDescription: Explore essential data structures including arrays, linked lists, stacks, and queues. Learn about time complexity and basic sorting algorithms with practical implementation examples.

resources.title: Modern Physics
resources.description: Quantum mechanics and relativity principles.
resources.fullDescription: Discover the fascinating world of modern physics including quantum theory, special relativity, and their implications in today's technological advancements.
